cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the problem of detecting mobile malware, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The paper proposes a new tool for detecting Android malware that leverages graph features of the API calls made by the apps, which involves techniques from software engineering (cs.SE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the performance of the tool using various datasets, which involves data analysis and statistics (cs.DS).
